THIS or THAT | @anua_global sunscreens

💚Heartleaf Silky Moisture Sun Cream
💛Zero Cast Moisturizing Finish Sunscreen

Common ground: no whitecast, both are chemical sunscreens, textures easy to blend, similar pricepoints

Star ingredient
💚houttuynia cordata extract (heartleaf) known for soothing properties
💛hyaluronic acid, glycerin, panthenol known for moisturizing properties

Texture and feel
💚Texture is almost lotion-like, lightweight
💛Texture is creamy, feels more moisturizing than the Heartleaf one

Best suited for
💚Combination to oily, acne prone skin that is looking for a sunscreen with a light texture and a glowy finish
💛Normal to dry skin that is looking for a sunscreen with a richer, more moisturizing feel and a dewy finish

TLDR
Texture (from light to rich) 💚<💛
Finish (from least to most dewy)💚<💛
Moisturizing (from light to rich)💚<💛
